import React from 'react'
import { Card, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'
import './titles.css'
export default function TitleGridItem() {
    return (
        <Card className='titleGridItem' style={{ width: '12rem', height: '14rem',marginTop:'1rem', marginLeft:'2rem'}}>
            <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/57/13/c8/5713c8fe95459ee7230191c0fb399afc.jpg" />
            <Card.Body style={{marginTop:'-1.25rem'}}>
                <Card.Title style={{ fontFamily: 'Open Sans', fontWeight: '600', marginLeft:'-1rem' }}>Run Forrest, Run!</Card.Title>
                <Card.Text style={{ fontFamily: 'Open Sans', fontWeight: '300', marginTop: '-10px' }}>
                    Fantasy/Drama
                </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    )
}
